HIGH-LEVEL ROADMAP
==================

v0.6	- XDG menu parser based on libmenu-cache ("jgmenu_run lx")
	- Icon cache on the fly
	- tint2 integration

v0.7	- On wake-up, check changes to .desktop files, tint2, xsettings,
	  jgmenurc, etc.

v0.8	- Add support for "fixed-position" items such as icons/images and
	  shapes (incl search box)

v0.9	- Enable pipemenu support and openbox menus

v1.0	- Create multi-window mode where submenus open in separate windows


AFTER v1.0
----------
  - Support for adding favourites in real-time (e.g. keyboard shortcut for
    locking menu-item onto the root menu - or similar)

  - Consider "hover" features and "inline expansion" of menus


